reviewText: What can I say about Dalene Kurtis except she is the hottest playmate ever!! If your a fan of Dalene's or just a fan of hot women, than this dvd is a must have!!!

I think Dalene Kurtis is so hot. The movie is pretty good but she is the best. I don't know about Playmate of the Year though. There were some really hot Playmates though. I see why she is PMOY, but there are so many who came close.
I put the video in for two minutes and they already got bare breasts plastered all over the screen! It's a shame you can't find good clean family entertainment these days.
The women in this video are full of silicone. They lack sensuality and sexuality. They have average bodies. The video scenes are contrived. Not up to Playboy's usual standards. Pass on this one.

It's maybe a first, but it seems that a breath of fresh air has overcome Playboy. I didn't hold much hope for something new with the Playmate of the year series, but it seems that they are trying to get away from short segments with an artist flair. It's not mind blowing but I came away with a good feeling after watching it and would recommend you give it a try. Plus Shanna Moakler is a goddess and not the cookie cutter playmate that seems to rule the magazine these days.
